## A+B+C FDD Pattern (≥4 sub-features, frontend/fullstack only)

**WHY**: A+B+C reduces duplication by 74% for features with many sub-features.
Backend is excluded because it already has a 2-tier pattern (BASE + per-sub).

```pseudo
if DESIGN_SCOPE == "backend":
    # A+B+C not applicable — backend uses BASE + per-sub pattern
elif HAS_SUBFEATURES and sub_feature_count >= 4:
    use_abc_pattern = true
    display("📋 Using A+B+C FDD Pattern (≥4 sub-features)")
else:
    use_abc_pattern = false
    display("📋 Using Traditional FDD Pattern (10 micro-agents)")
```

### A+B+C Document Structure

| Document | Agent | Purpose |
|----------|-------|---------|
| `{FEATURE}-portal-fdd.md` | portal-fdd-agent | Cross-feature workflows, user journeys, API strategy |
| `{FEATURE}-aggregate-fdd.md` | aggregate-fdd-agent | App shell, shared components, root state |
| `{FEATURE}-{SUB}-screens-fdd.md` | screens-fdd-agent | Module-specific screens (refs A & B) |

### Execution Order (A+B+C)

1. **Document A: Portal FDD** — Business workflows (Mermaid), user journeys (UJ-XXX), API strategy
2. **Document B: Aggregate FDD** — App shell & routing, shared components (SC-XXX), root state
3. **Document C: Screens FDD** (per sub) — Module screens (refs A), module state (refs B)

A+B+C agents: `specialists/document/detail-design-frontend/` (portal-fdd, aggregate-fdd, screens-fdd)

---

## Output Documents (scope-dependent)

| DESIGN_SCOPE | Documents per feature/sub-feature |
|-------------|----------------------------------|
| backend     | `{F}-{S}-backend-detail-design.md` (1 file) |
| frontend    | `{F}-{S}-frontend-detail-design.md` + optional `{F}-{S}-api-contracts.md` (1-2 files) |
| fullstack   | `{F}-{S}-frontend-detail-design.md` + `{F}-{S}-api-contracts.md` + `{F}-{S}-backend-detail-design.md` (3 files) |

## Document Standards
- **FDD Standard**: `.claude/docs/FRONTEND_DETAIL_DESIGN_STANDARD.md`
- **BDD Standard**: `.claude/docs/BACKEND_DETAIL_DESIGN_STANDARD.md`
- **API Standard**: `.claude/docs/API_CONTRACTS_STANDARD.md`

## Language Rules
- **Content**: Vietnamese (≥60% ratio)
- **Technical terms**: English (API, REST, JWT, Component, etc.)
- **Code snippets**: English (TypeScript/Java interfaces only, no implementation)

