*/design --detail Workflow v4.1*
*Self-contained micro-command with Stack Context + BASE + Post-Workflow*
*Scope-Aware: Backend / Frontend / Full-stack*
*Direct Agent Execution (No Orchestrator)*
*Enforcement: FDD (10 agents) + BDD (10 agents)*
*RAG 2.0: Preload (design+code layers) + Per-Agent (Graph+Specialists) + CALI (BDD) + Post-Gen Index*
*A+B+C Pattern: Frontend/Fullstack with ≥4 sub-features*
